Find roots from on Site to another in blantyre

Note: For the sites that are in remote areas, Google map may not recognize some path/root and might lead you to a location far from the site. To avoid this please enable Satellite view on the Google map which will give you a clear picture of where you are going. If the site and where Google map path stops are not close enough, consider using Satellite images.
